Does the corpus contain evidence that AI coding assistants eliminate the need for human code review?

Insufficient evidence in the current corpus.

To improve this answer, you could search for or add evidence on the effectiveness of AI-generated code in eliminating the need for human code review. For example, studies on the reliability and accuracy of AI-generated code, as well as the impact of AI-generated code on code quality and maintainability, could provide valuable insights.
